$ for an\nequivalent isotropically radiated power (EIRP) of 43 dBm up to a vehicle\nseparation distance of 200 m.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2017 01:58:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-21"}
